---
title: Chicken, Mushroom & Thyme Baked Risotto with Pear Salad
description: For a rich, creamy and delicious risotto without standing over the stove stirring, use your oven! This baked version features mushrooms and chicken thigh for lots of flavour, and has a fresh and easy salad on the side to lighten up the whole meal.  Dinner will never be the same again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-mushroom-thyme-baked-risotto-db4140df.jpg
